Gorgeous remodeled with light and bright kitchen including granite counters with center island and bar stoo breakfast overhang, stainless steel appliance, custom tile back-splas and tons of extra cabinets for storage. Great room style with vaulted ceilings and 16" tile flooring and gas fire place. Mountain views from Master family room and kitchen. Large office with double glass pane doors. Elegant stone and stucco exterior
